node.text:
A brief guide to doing the Inktober challenge.⁣
Special thanks to @artsnacks for making the #inktober2020 art box. I seriously love these art boxes!⁣ ⁣
⁣
To order one hit the link in the @inktober profile.⁣
⁣
-Jake

STAR PRINCESS AVEN⁣
⁣
Drew this on my flight back from the east coast. Tried to draw Aven from memory and ended up getting things a little wrong, but I like where it went.⁣
⁣
#starprincessaven #spacepunks #makingcomics #comiccharacter #characterdesign #robotart #albumcover #conceptartwork #comicartwork

node.text:
SKULL CHASER vs THE MOUTH of GRAAG!⁣
⁣
Been having fun with Skull lately. Thinking of stories and situations. I drew the blast from the gun and didn’t like how it turned out so you can see the correction tape mess where I covered it up.⁣
⁣
#skullchaser #spacepunks #peril #danger #comicart #copicmarkers #copicgasenfude #comiccharacter #mondays⁣

node.text:
TWEETBOT.⁣
⁣
I did this for @tycarterart’s new “Artist in Residence” project he’s doing for Patreon. Each month Ty interviews an artist then the do a demo in real time and walk you through their process. You can watch me make this drawing from start to finish. It took me about 30 minutes and I tell all my tricks.⁣
⁣
I also walk you through my Snakemech drawing I did a few weeks ago. Good stuff, check it out!⁣
⁣
Go to @tycarterart and support his Patreon, link in his bio and my story.⁣
⁣
#tweetbot #twitterbot #birdrobo #twitter #comicart #comicartist #digitalart #robotart #mech #mecha #conceptsketch #conceptart

node.text:
SKULL vs MAIMOTH⁣
⁣
I was going to draw a Dinosaur monster and my kid (Calvin the Art Director) said I draw too many dinosaurs and to make it a mammoth monster. The kid is always right.⁣
⁣
Skull’s running pose was inspired by @philbourassa’s Impulse character sheet. I’m constantly in awe of Phil’s incredible poses he draws. ⁣
⁣

node.text:
SKULL CHASER TEES! ⁣
🔗 in bio: @jakeparker⁣
⁣
Skull Chaser, inter-galactic corpse of mystery. He's not after power, he doesn't want to get rich, he just wants to watch the criminal underworld burn.⁣
⁣
I salute the genius who invented the t-shirt. This individual wanted to cover their upper body with a simple one piece garment, but who also wanted look cool doing so and in the process created the greatest invention of the 20th century.⁣
⁣
I'm feeling a little inspired, so I'm  throwing my hat in the ring and making some shirts of my own now. ⁣
⁣
Wearing this shirt might not make you an inter-galactic bounty hunter, but you'll feel cool that's for sure...and at the end of the day what more could you want?⁣
⁣
Product details:⁣
⁣
- This is a pre-order. Pre-order ends June 27th. Shirts ship in early August⁣
- Waterbased ink printed on  100% airlume combed and ringspun cotton.⁣
- Soft, permanent silkscreen printing. Not print on demand.⁣
- Unisex only⁣
🔗 in bio: @jakeparker ⁣
 ⁣

node.text:
🐍🤖⁣
⁣
Snake mech design for a comic I’m working on.⁣
⁣
How’s everybody been? I just checked my account and was shocked that I haven’t posted in OVER A MONTH.⁣
⁣
If you’re seeing this post it must mean I somehow beat the algorithm. Ha. ⁣
⁣
Been so busy with childrensbookpro.com and camping and my daughter’s graduation I didn’t realize how much time had past not being on here.⁣
⁣
Honestly, it’s been nice not to have this app own me.⁣
⁣
So….See you next month! 😚⁣
⁣
-Jake ⁣
⁣
